Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\NI want you to keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello everyone, I'm Yuri Killian.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today is the day the\NCircus Festival will take place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three years ago, on this\Nday, I was here with Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And our glory also started from here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.78,0:00:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, my partner is Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way to erase the\Nmistakes I made in the past,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.49,0:00:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but this time I intend to do everything in\Nmy power for Sora, Layla, and Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, I wonder if Sora really\Ncan tolerate this cruel stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:01:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Cruel Amazing Festival."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school Yuri's attending\Nshould be around here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we stop here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then, one more hour.\NThen let's end today's training.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resting is another part \Nof practice, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is the practice room\Nfor the school Yuri is attending.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of maneuver are they working on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm glad to know Sora is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mute and Miss Alice,\Nthank you for helping us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome. By the way,\Ncan we come tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We learned a lot. So, \Nplease? Say it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're nice enough \Nto offer their help,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's impolite to say no. Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please come and help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I'll walk you to your hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but I didn't book a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.04,0:04:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you stay at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... but... it's like\NI'm asking you too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hi, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I was... taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're breathing hard. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if you need a place\Nto stay, I'll find a place for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't bother me even\None bit if you stay at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Sora is a part of the Kaleido Stage cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage will look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you've got a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So shall we charge the room to Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Please charge it to me, Ken Robbins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And please keep this secret from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An angel's maneuver.\NI'll make sure to perfect it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm going to win. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess the ones I need to\Nwatch out for are Mr. & Mrs. Patrova
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the street performer \Npair, Mute and Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did refine my Demon\NSpiral even further, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be the victors, no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to compete against the\Nmaneuvers of the world's top stars,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and yet I'm not quite fired up. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something is missing. I wonder why.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to force a jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel out the moment when your\Nbody gains the most power, then jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:06:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And maintain a beautiful pose as you go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware of your weak point?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Ken told me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I've only been doing big\Nmaneuvers, my body's unbalanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But even with only the\Nbasics they teach at circus school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you shouldn't lose this much balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Japan, there are hardly any\Ncircus schools, so I haven't gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think she was able to perform\Nthe legendary great maneuver without...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard. I'll endure\Nit no matter how tough it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This maneuver is called \Nthe "Angel's Maneuver"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it gives the\Nimpression of weightlessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like the feathers of an angel's wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a ballerina, in order to\Nmake your body seem light as a feather
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and maintain a beautiful pose, you\Nneed strong grounding in the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even endured Mr. Leon's\Nspecial training and passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I did then,\Nno matter how tough it gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover for my lack of\Nbasics through force of will!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, when it's you saying it,\NI start to feel like you really can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Then, let's continue practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to master my timing.\NAnd I have to pose beautifully.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's Sora's name registered?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her partner is Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... there was that method.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she still hasn't given up on victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know now... what was \Nmissing in this festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora... it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, try to knock me \Ndown by crashing into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please crash into my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was this close too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow! Pay more attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Spiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her move has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this feeling? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hardly wait for the festival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to compete with\NSora in the festival, soon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to compete with Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In only a few days, she\Nmanaged to reach this point...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impressive as ever. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:09:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, if she can just\Nmaintain that beautiful pose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing... I've never seen that maneuver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really looks like an angel's wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can do this! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The day has finally come.\NEverything will be determined today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, Miss Sarah, you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Un, deux, trois, un, deux, trois...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}un chien! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Charlie. He's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she was able to meet\Nthe clown she admired, Mr. Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, it's been a long time, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming. I know\Ntraveling expenses are not cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're concerned about travel expenses,\NMiss Sarah negotiated that with the Boss for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So all expenses are paid by Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I'm the only one paying\Neverything out of my own pocket.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I guess there's nothing I can do now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, make sure you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can participate in the\Nfestival together three years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.06,0:10:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to bring my good luck pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I might be done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's Yuri Killian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should stay in retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The partner he's with...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she the girl who paired with Layla\NHamilton in that legendary great maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're a pair of big shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I see you don't\Nknow when to give up either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not lose to the two of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri Killian...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. Long time, no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you meet each other when you \Nparticipated in the festival three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever thought that we'd\Nsee each other at this place again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps a match with you\Nis my unavoidable destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you want to pair with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With me as I am now, the\None they call the God of Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You taught me what I need to\Ndo to climb to the top in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should place more\Nvalue in your current partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between\NLeon and Mr. Yuri three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't know. I don't. I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, maybe, you don't\Nknow that Miss Layla is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. To present the trophy to the winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which one of us is going\Nto receive the trophy from Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, for the opening of\Nthis International Circus Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd like the previous winner,\NMiss Layla Hamilton, to say a few words!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a very cruel place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's also a step forward that we\Ncan't take unless we overcome this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compete with each other,\Ntrain each other, improve each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in order to take the\Nfirst step toward your dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,give this everything you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry. My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I see they don't call you\Nthe God of Death for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you destroy your partner,\Nyou're certainly not destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entry No. 5, Mr. & Mrs. Patrova.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. & Mrs. Patrova always look\Nlike such a happily married couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very soon, it will be May and Leon's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then after that, it will be Mute and Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Sora's turn will be after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... This is more nerve-wracking\Nthan when I'm in competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:14:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you want some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Since Mr. Mute and \NAlice aren't here yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them alone.\NDon't worry about other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they helped me practice every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happened\Nto them because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Did you exploit your rivals' goodwill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, that's not half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong. I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Don't pretend to be\Nlittle Miss Goody Two-Shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it's the same\Nas if you used them, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if they just didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll step out and check on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being late. No. 8, Mute and Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready and stand by in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mute and Miss Alice, \NI'm glad you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nice... costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you look like... angels...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.55,0:16:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us, but we will do the\NAngel's Maneuver before you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you used us,\Ndon't you think it's only fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I never meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think we'd just\Nhelp you with good intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to make everyone's\Ndream come true, we cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did nothing against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt a little sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... but I think I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, don't screw up the timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't win this year,\Nwe don't have another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. I hate that Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, after Layla Hamilton retired,\Nthey had to send two pairs this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, our dream broke into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is wrong. This is that kind of world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were prepared for this, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's almost time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a very cruel place. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But there's also a step forward that we\Ncan't take unless we overcome this place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And in order to take the\Nfirst step towards my dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of maneuver is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can he grab her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even more amazing than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hall is dead silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's been enchanted by a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By a demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this? I feel out of place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It should be the same applause as usual,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm afraid to win this applause.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}During the practice,\Nwe almost managed perfection.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, we're going to perfect this here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can do it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Angel's Maneuver... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, this isn't even close\Nto the Angel's Maneuver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mute, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mute...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mute...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We never thought of imitating someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, because you suddenly\Ndecided to participate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to win in the festival\Nand get the world's attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and organize a performance team\Nwith these guys right here, and travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us, but we will do the\NAngel's Maneuver before you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it's same as\Nif you used them, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, our dream\Nbroke into pieces. Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. This isn't the place I was aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage I was aiming for is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage I saw with my mother\Nand father was more fun, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should never have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel's Maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I heard about it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel's Maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora... Is she crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the Angel's Maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know Kaleido Stage\Nhad that kind of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why she quit in the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she did it all the way\Nthrough, she might have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? Did she just give up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mastering the Angel's \NManeuver to that extent...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you withdrew. \NYou're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You disgraced the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ran away from the stage\Nwhere a serious match was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought walking Miss Layla's\Npath could take me to my dream,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I don't know anymore. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I aim for? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All kinds of hard luck flocks\Nyour way as if it's spurring you on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swept away by it, time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.72,0:22:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as predicted, take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:23:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will get you out right away {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.91,0:23:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forcibly only (Drive with the fastest speed){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view I look down at every day is the best{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Escape for the sake of tomorrow {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I don't have a vacation, \NI've got an oasis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn off the cell \Nphone and charge my love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because some pain,\Nyou can't soothe with just kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone, we pass each other by{\i0}
